==============================================================================
SECTION 1 — DEFINITIONS
==============================================================================

“Model” refers to the LoRA adapter weights, configuration files, tokenizer
files, and associated inference scripts released in this repository.

“Generated Output” refers to any text, evaluation, score, JSON response, or
other output produced by running the Model or the Gradio application.

“Non-Commercial Use” means any use that is not intended for, or directed toward,
commercial advantage or monetary compensation.

“Commercial Use” means any use of the Model, the Gradio application, or the
Generated Output in a product, service, system, or workflow that generates
revenue (directly or indirectly), including consultancy, subscription,
evaluation services, SaaS tools, internal organizational systems, or
integrations that contribute to monetized activities.

