SECTION 6 — ETHICAL USE REQUIREMENTS
==============================================================================

Users agree NOT to:
- use the Model to manipulate funding outcomes;
- suppress reviewers or retaliate against individuals;
- conduct surveillance of reviewers or research actors;
- generate harmful, biased, or discriminatory outputs intentionally;
- misrepresent the capabilities or limitations of the Model.

A human reviewer must remain in the loop for all evaluation or decision-making.

